{"tid":129284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成報：管理層人身安全受嚴重威脅已報警","createTime":"2017-02-21T12:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T00:42:31.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5df3cf61e3d7265215dcae0ed3a6914dc567d04","tid":129284,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"成報：管理層人身安全受嚴重威脅已報警<br />\n2017-02-21 HKT 19:59<br />\n<br />\n成報發出緊急聲明，指公司管理層的人身安全受到嚴重威脅，又說相信事件是與該報刊出評論作者「漢江泄」的系列文章所致。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，有人採取極端方式攻擊成報，包括在成報管理層住所附近，四處張貼附印相關人員相片的恐嚇及抹黑單張。照片經比對後，極大機會取自回鄉證照片，質疑相關照片只有香港中國旅行社及公安部等發證機關才可擁有，現時流入不法人士手中，相信是跨境犯罪，事件對當事人造成恐慌及困擾，已立即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n成報又指，自2月中突然有大批可疑人士、貌似內地人在辦公大樓地下門外及部分管理層的住所外，長時間跟蹤、偷拍，另外成報網站遭到密集式攻擊，在本月18日及19日曾經被攻擊至短暫停頓。<br />\n<br />\n成報指今次事件是政治威嚇，而事件發生在臨近香港特首選舉之際，懷疑是有關人士意圖迫令成報停止刊登評論文章，意圖操控選舉結果，案件已交由警方處理。<br />\n<br />\n成報在聲明中指，壓力雖大，但無畏無懼，會繼續發聲。"},{"pid":"838006f55b5a2ebea87c07835aff9596e72b0629","tid":129284,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab4e5ad0db81c2a091f2b96be2d0b4d7e2195ed","tid":129284,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"我們都是成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1750db8b13beb008eabb8a181042a7b3c0a927f","tid":129284,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"無畏無懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36d2b2d39894e5addb1ce992c8af16d7f5c3566","tid":129284,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"江派一系搵人搞漢江泄?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8044e1fcafc3031ae5a891595cc03b3121aa17f0","tid":129284,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"又話有習做後台既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4950525e5ffa7d25642021cebb0cf1e98630f5","tid":129284,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話有習做後台既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知山高皇帝遠? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e682d4488c5b4c0d5bc408b476625f01092913","tid":129284,"uid":7432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"其實成報後始係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df8caea1df274be9ca2ec0beb3625661348ab9d","tid":129284,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cdc401df32365947dfb033c939876a70b9d216","tid":129284,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"成報係時候出皇牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a690bca8a87d3573ab683a6eecbdcff7a2eeb8f","tid":129284,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成報係時候出皇牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499e6adf3b0fc47f8cf93fc110ab57d0d48d6528","tid":129284,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【邏輯推演】泛民選委應該同時提名胡國興葉劉淑儀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"ed0978e2abb7647263c73fecc52e21d996f5c8a1","tid":129284,"uid":86408,"like":0,"dislike